<emphasis bold="true" box="[165,400,803,837]" pageId="279" pageNumber="884">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
The Yunnan 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1911" box="[596,740,803,837]" class="Mammalia" family="Muridae" genus="Hadromys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="279" pageNumber="884" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Hadromys</taxonomicName>
