<subSubSection pageId="279" pageNumber="884" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="279.[165,1371,728,1073]" pageId="279" pageNumber="884">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[167,519,886,915]" pageId="279" pageNumber="884">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List. The Yunnan 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1911" box="[230,374,925,954]" class="Mammalia" family="Muridae" genus="Hadromys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="279" pageNumber="884" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Hadromys</taxonomicName>
seems to be rare, and its natural history and conservation threats need to be studied.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
